              #tablets.tab-pane
                p.tittles-pages Mascotas
                .row
                  .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-3
                    .thumbnail.thumbnail-content-phones
                      img.img-responsive(src='assets/img/tablet.png' alt='Tablet')
                      .caption
                        h3.text-center(name='name_pet') Mascota
                        p.text-justify
                          | Datos de la mascota
                        p.text-center
